THIMBLE
THEATRE
has

no
competitive
ambitions
with
professional
theatres
or
show

houses.
It
has
one
purpose
and
one
aim:
to
give
the
American

the
American

the
American

the
American

a
chance

American

Charles

Little
Thimble

exploited
